{
  "stem": "18626.10",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That Professor Schilling, he was the-- one of the inventors who invented the analysis of the [GERMAN] test.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that professor made all kind of tests on human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a old man, almost-- [SIGHS] maybe about 75 years, with a long, little beard, very frail, skinny-looking.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was then called to the stand after the girls came, you know, and told what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They called the professor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was between the 40 criminals on the stand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was called.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he says, yeah, he did make the experiments because he wanted for the world the health, and for life to improve.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's why he was experimenting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would be in contact with him, maybe I wouldn't have been alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because most people who were in contact with that man, they never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I, I saw one time they took a priest out in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was laying right not far from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to me-- and I was-- that time, I was sick with my pleurisy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a little sick, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what sickness it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was, like, laying right close by me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they took him out in the middle of the night, he touched me on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, Moses, God help you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't think you'll see again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But God knows everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He never came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He must've taken him away for experiments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trial began, I think, November 15, if I don't mistake, 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I bought-- I was brought with American, with MP.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could have-- if I wanted, I couldn't have been after I testified.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could have gone away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
